{"word":"G2720 - κατευθύνω - kateuthýnō - kat-yoo-thoo'-no - Guide","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κατευθύνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kateuthýnō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-yoo-thoo'-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Guide</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வழிநடத்து"},{"paragraph":"to make straight, guide, direct"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2590 - καρπός - karpós - kar-pos'/2590\">G2590</a> and <a href=\"#/G2116 - εὐθύνω - euthýnō - yoo-thoo'-no/2116\">G2116</a>; to <i>straighten fully</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>direct:</i> - guide, direct.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}